6avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Vika Felmetsger","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"[~kmeredith], here's my take on how to position SELinux:\r\n{quote}\r\nSELinux is an important security mechanism. It allows to confine user and processes to only access system resources authorized by well-defined policies. This allows to limit the extend of system compromise if a user or a process is compromised. \r\n\r\nEucalyptus services ship with a set of SELinux policies for RHEL 7. Eucalyptus services will run in a confined mode if SELinux is enabled and set to enforcing mode on a host they are running on. Enabling SELinux is particularly important for NC and UFS hosts as they are more likely to be externally reachable over network. On NC, SELinux also provides an additional layer of isolation between guest VMs as well as a hypervisor by individually confining them to their own domains.\r\n{quote}\r\nLet me know if that's sufficient or you're looking for something else. Thanks!","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=rusvika","name":"rusvika","key":"rusvika","accountId":"557058:0f138bdf-f1d0-4468-9edd-e45575af47da","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Vika Felmetsger","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2017-02-01T15:49:20.484-0600","updated":"2017-02-01T15:49:20.484-0600"}],"maxResults":1,"total":1,"startAt":0},"worklog":{"startAt":0,"maxResults":20,"total":0,"worklogs":[]},"customfield_11808":null}}